Swiss Theory Prep — third-party asset notices
=============================================

This project is a personal Swiss Cat. B driving theory prep PWA. The
application code is original work. The third-party assets bundled in
public/ are catalogued below with their upstream source and licence.
No CC-BY-SA, CC-BY-NC, or all-rights-reserved assets are included —
the entire asset graph is CC0 / public domain so the repo can ship
without attribution-cascade obligations on derivative work.


